AMAPIANO leading DJ and producer DJ Maphorisa impressed his fans after using a $100 bill to crush his weed. The Banyana hitmaker crushed weed on the dollar and the people around him were taking a video of him. He was flexing and preparing the weed on top of the money. The note he was using is equal to about R1 559. ALSO READ : CHRIS RADEBE FALLING IN LOVE WITH LERATO MVELASE However, unlike the impressed fans who were recording his video, people who saw the video on social media said he was wasting a lot of money. Mr Quarantine commented: “Uyadelela lomfana.” Another Twitter user, Nonny, wrote: “Saze savelelwa.” “R1 562,70 kanjalo nje? Yoh!!” wrote PhonicBass_DJ. See the video below. DJ Maphorisa uses $100 to crush weed. pic.twitter.com/TA7GTJKR61 